  "remarks": "LLC IQ Components is a Russian importer of electronic components. The company delivers products such as semiconductor and microwave components from abroad to the largest Russian military-industrial complex enterprises that manufacture equipment used in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, LLC IQ Components is supporting materially the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
